Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91821,93489}Good evening. Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:34.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93489,94824}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94824,96951}Why are you inside Sam's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96951,98536}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98536,100580}Sam Carraclough's\Nhouse is next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:41.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100580,101205}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:45.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104834,105918}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106669,109339}I'll be damned. Is it you, George?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109339,112759}I've been away for a moment\Nand look how much you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112759,115637}You were just a baby\Nlast time we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115637,119182}Excuse me, sir, but haven't you\Nconfused me with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:02.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119182,122101}Have I made a mistake again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122685,126314}My name's John, not George.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126314,129233}Let me think. John, John…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129233,132612}I'm pretty sure that Sam Carraclough's\Nson was named George…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133112,135907}Oh? I guess that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135907,137033}But I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137033,138660}Oh? Mr. Dohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139911,141829}It's been ages, Melissa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141829,144207}Sam is upstairs.\NI'll call him in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147126,148628}How do I put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152382,154217}Oh, what a wonderful dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154217,156260}Its hair is absolutely splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157136,158388}What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158388,159389}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160348,162141}At this hour, on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162141,164519}Am I being a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164519,165520}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165520,168856}Really? Thank goodness.\NI'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169107,170650}Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170650,173111}I feel like I had seen\Nhim somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173111,174737}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174737,176698}He's the director of the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176698,177573}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177573,179867}That man, such a big shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180410,181536}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181536,184288}Don't judge people\Nfrom the way they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184288,187875}Naturally, don't judge them\Nby their job titles alone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188751,190586}So the question is when?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190586,191921}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191921,194173}It was all decided so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194173,195633}I just got a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195633,199178}They'll come by plane tomorrow\Nand begin the inspection at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,201556}It's very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201556,202807}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202807,204392}Which is why I came to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204892,206394}By plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210690,212191}An airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212191,213943}I wonder who's arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213943,215194}Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216195,219991}Speaking of airplanes…\NDo you remember that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220825,221993}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222285,226080}When we met for the first time,\Nthere was an airplane as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252607,254400}So awesome.{NOTE:retrospection}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258321,260239}Hey, stay away from the bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260239,261991}Hey, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261991,265036}It's not mine, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:28.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268122,268956}Hey, it's a…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270124,271584}What is it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271584,273669}Whose dog is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283262,284472}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286474,288518}Come on, come here…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291604,293940}All's good now.\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296692,299654}If it wasn't for that airplane,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299654,302740}we might never have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303825,305868}To think that such a small puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305868,309247}could grow into such a large\NRough Collie in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310122,312750}You've grown into\None big sleepyhead, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313960,315795}The sky, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:21.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317213,321759}I wish I could fly in the sky\Nsome day, even if just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334564,336732}Now I remembered\Nwho was on that plane…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345616,347743}Who was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348411,349328}Hey, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350288,352206}Oh, you're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371726,374228}Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374228,375479}Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375479,379108}I wish we had a red carpet\Nfor these situations…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379525,381235}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381235,383988}As long as we're polite\Nand the place is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384322,385573}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385573,388075}I saw in the newspaper\Nthat movie theaters do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,390661}They roll the carpet out\Nand welcome the top brass on it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390661,391996}What are those notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391996,393539}Put them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393539,395249}They're so unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398961,401088}There's quite a commotion above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401088,402089}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402089,403758}One of the stakeholders is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404425,407428}The director never shows his face\Naround the office nor the shaft,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:51.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407428,411140}and look how flustered he is today.\NWhy is he licking someone's shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411140,414226}You goof. The director has his\Nown superiors that can fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414226,415645}He's just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415645,418856}You're forgetting that he\Ndoesn't have any rights to the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418856,419899}The owners, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419899,421525}Whatever, just help me\Npush this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430576,431953}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:18.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433746,438167}It's rare to see you here\Nso early on a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438167,439085}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439085,440586}Are you here to\Nhelp us with Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440586,443214}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443631,446133}"No, not really", he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446133,449720}Lassie is a good sheepdog.\NShe'll help us out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450012,452306}Lassie is Lassie.\NI am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452306,454725}Don't be like that.\NHere, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455226,456310}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456310,458521}This little lamb always gets lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458521,460898}Can you look after it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460898,463526}I'd rather look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463526,464235}The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:52.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467196,472576}Oh, Lord. Will be really fine\Nwithout any red carpets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472576,476747}Let's pretend you are serious.\NWhere do you expect to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477623,480251}What if you run\Nto the nearest store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480251,482003}What? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482003,484255}What kind of store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484255,485673}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485673,488592}It's just an ordinary place of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488592,490511}He expects to see\Nno less, and no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490678,493389}Yes, yes, but still…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494098,495516}Ah! Sam, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495516,496350}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496350,498394}That is no good.\NThat is no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498394,501063}We can't have him\Ndo that out in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505317,507319}What a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508487,509488}Bansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509488,510740}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510740,512616}This is my fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513200,516954}I know you're good at your job\Nno matter how much you drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516954,519540}but if you don't mind, go someplace\Nwhere nobody can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519540,520374}Pff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522543,524211}– He's here already?\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524211,526130}That rich bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530134,531385}It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531385,532928}It's coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532928,535181}What's that?\NWho's flying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535181,537224}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537224,539018}It's the same airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552156,553365}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553365,555201}Isn't it going to land?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562416,563959}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565127,566879}The sheep are blocking their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566879,567922}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569006,571509}Hey, buddy. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576972,578307}Ah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578307,579892}Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580768,582728}Gather the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594990,597868}Move. Move!\NI'm telling you to move, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598619,601038}– Wait!\N– Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602206,604208}No! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:04.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604208,604834}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609713,612508}What are going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612508,614135}Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649795,652882}I am going to the mine, Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652882,655342}Head back to the mansion before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655676,658846}Oh? Are you not going\Nto take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659346,663267}I am only going to verify whether\Nmy employees are doing their jobs properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663267,665853}You go play with your new horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674361,678532}My grandfather is always like that,\Nnot caring an ounce about people's feelings.
Comment: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:25.33,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:685331,685331}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691003,692671}I saw you from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:36.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692671,696050}You are the one who gathered the sheep\Nso that we could land. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696634,699136}It is time for us to leave, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:43.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699136,703265}If it were not for this dog,\Nwe would not be able to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703265,704683}We should thank it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704683,706685}Does this pasture\Nbelong to that town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706685,708145}Hm? A town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708437,710231}Oh, over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710231,713943}I should pay attention to my\Nsurroundings more closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713943,715736}Are you living there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716904,718072}Good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718614,720574}It is time to go, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720950,722284}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722284,723244}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727081,729291}It's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733837,736090}You're such a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738008,741220}In the end I didn't see\Nthe plane landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742763,743889}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:32.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749270,752189}Lassie… Is she that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752898,754149}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775504,778048}Last time I checked,\Nwe weren't soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778048,781302}The owner is a general,\Nand we're his army.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781302,782011}Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782011,785180}This is too much. We pulled\Neveryone away from their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:09.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785639,789059}I thought cleaning the place\Nwould be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789059,792688}I'd never guess\Nhe'd ask everyone to line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794648,796692}What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:30.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,810539}How do you like it, milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810539,812958}It's nice, but a bit boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812958,816128}Oh, I was referring\Nto this beautiful horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816128,819882}I have groomed his coat for hours\Njust for you, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819882,822217}His coat is beautiful, I admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822760,824470}But can he run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824470,826680}Of course he can, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826680,828682}If you like, he can even gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829850,831393}All right, let me try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831393,832561}Wh-Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832561,834313}To the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835773,839068}But the weather\Nis about to get worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839068,841236}Ah, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:05.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841236,845574}She seriously thinks he can gallop that far?\NShe doesn't know the first thing about horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845574,847910}I don't care if she\Nhas to go back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850704,851538}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:20.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856710,860089}Come on, it's okay, alright?\NIt's just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860089,861590}No, it's not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861590,864009}We are leaving immediately\Nonce the inspection is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:28.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864009,868806}But you could take me for a quick flight\Naround the area while you're waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869556,871725}No means no, lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:35.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871725,875104}What's the problem?\NYou old skinflint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875104,876313}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:37.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877147,877981}Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877981,879358}Let's run for it, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880734,883862}Why did Heinz lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884947,886949}You can't run well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886949,889660}It was too early for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:54.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891078,894915}But that brown dog\Ncould run so well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898544,901755}We're almost at the town.\NLet's go slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:07.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906760,907636}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908345,910639}The houses stay one behind another,\Nwithout any opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911807,914476}How does one\Nget inside the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920858,923819}All I wanted was\Njust one short trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924528,927322}Whatever. Let's take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930868,934079}Are those the houses\Nof the mine employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934079,936290}I wonder where is\Nthe shepherd's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983086,984796}It's raining…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:27.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984796,987049}We can't go anywhere like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987049,988717}Where was it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988717,989718}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990135,992804}That was the last one\NI got from Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994806,996475}Come here, Mr. Hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996475,997726}I won't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999811,1002105}It got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002105,1003357}Are you going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009279,1010405}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013367,1014910}Your voice is so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014910,1016954}You're the girl from that plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019873,1021041}Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022834,1023877}Wanna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:06.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026088,1026964}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032928,1035222}I'm finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037224,1039518}Group II is operating back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039518,1040936}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:24.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040936,1044898}I'm so glad that I got here\Nbefore the rain got stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044898,1046024}So much mud…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046024,1048235}Yes, work piles up as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048235,1050737}In addition, the director\Nis all trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050737,1053240}He's in the next room,\Nlooking like he's going to black out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056243,1057536}I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:43.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058704,1063542}He urged the owner to come visit us\Nwith his granddaughter next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063542,1065335}Oh? His granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065335,1069006}The Radling's pride and joy,\Nhis cute granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069006,1071300}I can't imagine how spoiled\Nthat girl must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078223,1079474}Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079850,1081893}Yes, it's very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081893,1083186}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083186,1085939}It's the best candy in Colin's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085939,1086732}Colin's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086732,1089568}Yes, they have a store\Nnear the town square.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091361,1094740}The only place to sell candy\Nin this town is at his family's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095407,1097492}They also have jam\Nand canned goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098869,1100495}So it's a candy store?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:26.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100996,1106460}Yes. But they also sell medicines,\Nseeds and work as a post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:27.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106460,1107628}A busy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108670,1111798}Yes. They also do the deliveries\Nand take requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111798,1114760}Even today Colin couldn't play\Nwith me because of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115177,1116136}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116136,1118055}I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118055,1119056}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119056,1121516}Colin likes to work\Naround the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:46.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121516,1126688}When there are no customers,\Nhe just reads his favorite books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126688,1129358}I see. He likes reading, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129358,1131193}Yes, he reads a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131193,1134279}His favorite are adventure books.\NHe always begins with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136365,1137908}What made you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137908,1140410}Because Colin's…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:04.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140410,1144498}Whenever someone enters the store,\Nhe gets freaked out and tries to hide the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144498,1146166}It's just too funny to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146166,1147709}Why does he hide the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:13.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147709,1153298}Colin likes the books to the point\Nwhere he reads the ones sold in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153298,1156385}So he thinks it's bad to read the goods\Nhe sells in front of the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156385,1158637}But no one cares about it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:34.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170524,1174736}I have recently borrowed one of\Nthose adventure books from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:38.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174736,1178323}It was fun, although\Nsome parts were difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178323,1179533}What kind of book?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179533,1182327}"Five Weeks in a Balloon"\Nby Jules Verne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182327,1186832}When I read it, I thought, "this is it",\Nand I wish I could fly in the sky some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189459,1191086}You came here\Nby an airplane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:51.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191086,1191920}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191920,1194589}I don't have an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194589,1197884}But I know a place where it feels\Nlike you can almost touch the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197884,1198719}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198719,1200679}It's called Rocky Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200679,1202848}– Rocky Castle?\N– That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202848,1206017}It's to the south of our town,\Nfar in the moorland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206017,1208186}It's a large rock formation\Nthat looks like a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:12.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208186,1212524}When you reach the top of it,\Nyou can see the whole sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212941,1214025}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:19.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214025,1219948}When I think about it, it would be my fault\Nif she fell off the horse and hurt herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222659,1225036}She's traveled that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225662,1228290}Milady. Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228957,1231793}Oh, no, he is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:35.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232002,1235797}Please stop kidding around.\NI will get punished, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236465,1237591}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237591,1238967}I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238967,1240802}Hey, just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241303,1243096}I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243096,1244139}Open your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245140,1246308}Come on, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247184,1248351}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248351,1251813}Cover it with your other hand\Nso that it doesn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253106,1254941}Something's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254941,1256818}You can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260906,1262324}It looks like a gem, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262949,1264326}It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264326,1266244}It is more beautiful than any jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266244,1267829}Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268538,1269498}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270248,1272959}I am sorry, Heinz,\NI gave you trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272959,1274461}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276046,1277923}Look who just got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277923,1278965}She's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279466,1280217}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280217,1282969}I just realized\NI still don't know her name…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:26.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283720,1286097}I forgot to ask his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289059,1290602}That brown dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291645,1293480}It's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293480,1295190}What are you saying, milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295190,1297859}We have to go back\Nbefore I get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300028,1301696}Yes. I understand.
