Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319464,1321091}{\i1}Trouble, trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:04.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321091,1324553}{\i1}Lassie, that girl's here.\NShe came to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:08.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324553,1328098}{\i1}Oh? She's already getting along\Nwell with Sandy and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328098,1329391}{\i1}But something's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329391,1332102}{\i1}How did she know where I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332102,1334604}{\i1}Next episode:\N"Our First Cake".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334604,1336022}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
